overview:
One man’s adventure in Buenos Aires, Argentina as he attempts to go from tourist to townie.

Go deeper than your average travel blog as Gareth Leonard takes you through his journey of learning the language, meeting the people and adapting to the South American culture.

This travel site is honest, adventurous and entertaining. Tourist2townie.com also includes travel services, gear and advice for anyone thinking about traveling to Buenos Aires, Argentina or anywhere else in the world.

Enjoy.
